I can't say for certain without reviewing the info, but I'm 99% sure that the lockout chip is the only difference.  They <em>might</em> require a RAM expansion in the NES, if they use RAM at $0800+ and above.  I don't know if they would even do that, depends on the game.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=10">Memblers</a> — Fri Mar 05, 2010 1:31 pm</p><hr />
